metadata.title: Skinomi Screen Protector Compatible with ViewSonic G Tablet Clear TechSkin TPU Anti-Bubble HD Film
features: The TechSkin screen protector compatible with ViewSonic G Tablet is specifically designed using precise laser cutting technology to offer maximum screen coverage. Material flexibility allows total coverage even on curved devices
Self-Healing, flexible, tough, military-grade thermoplastic urethane, designed to absorb impact. The TechSkin is resistant against scratches, punctures, UV light and will not yellow
Easy, error-proof, and anti-bubble installation. Liquid solution allows adjustments during installation. Significantly reduces dust, oil and fingerprint smudges
Optically transparent, virtually invisible, and HD Clear screen protector with smooth glass-like surface and "True Touch" feel. A great alternative to a typical "static cling" PET screen protector
Lifetime Warranty from Manufacturer. Made in the USA. Includes original Skinomi TechSkin Screen Protector compatible with the ViewSonic G Tablet
description: The ViewSonic G Tablet Screen Protector is the clear choice for maximum scratch protection. The ViewSonic G Tablet Screen Protector goes beyond your traditional ViewSonic G Tablet screen protectors, skins, covers, and cases. TechSkin is made from the same film material used to protect luxury cars, military aircrafts, and NASA space shuttles. The ViewSonic G Tablet Screen Protector is custom made to specifically fit the ViewSonic G Tablet. ViewSonic G Tablet Screen Protector Features: • Toughest clear protective film in the market • Clear protection that is virtually invisible • Preserves your ViewSonic G Tablet's original design • Protects your ViewSonic G Tablet from scratches, dents, and physical wear-and-tear • Patented layer of UV protection for anti-yellowing • Provides protection without affecting the functions of your ViewSonic G Tablet • Non-sticky or restrictive outer surface Included: • ViewSonic G Tablet Screen Protector • 1 Bottle of Application Solution • Installation Instructions • Lifetime Warranty Compatible with:ViewSonic G Tablet The ViewSonic G Tablet Screen Protector features two layers of protection. The first, topmost layer contains no unsightly "orange peel effect," while providing scratch-resistance and UV protection for anti-yellowing. The second layer is a thick, puncture resistant film to minimize damage from scrapes and dents. Unlike other ViewSonic G Tablet screen protectors and skins, the TechSkin features "self-healing" technology, meaning scratches do not stay on the film, and keeps your ViewSonic G Tablet looking new. For installation instructions and video please see: TechSkin Installation Instructions*Lifetime Warranty for this product is offered by the Skinomi.com, please contact Skinomi or review the FAQ section for more information regarding the warranty policy.WARNING: As with any electronic device, exposing it to excessive water or other fluids may cause harm to the device. Skinomi will not be responsible for any damage to the device caused by excessive water or improper application of the TechSkin.
